                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is very like &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-26665&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;SPARK-26665&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
